# Database Rules (Prisma)

## Access Patterns
- No DB access in UI components
- All DB logic lives in `/server/services`

## Query Patterns
- Avoid N+1 queries
- Prefer joins/includes
- No looped DB calls
- Batch operations when possible

## Reliability
- All critical operations must be idempotent
- Use transactions for multi-step operations
- Structured logging only (no console.log)
